query.query: {"pigql":"q = load \"AnnualRentObligationReport\";q = filter q by 'EXPENSE_INCOME' != \"INCOME\";q = filter q by {{ column(REGION_1.selection, [\"REGION\"]).asEquality('REGION') }};q = filter q by {{ column(FISCAL_YEAR_5.selection, [\"FISCAL_YEAR\"]).asEquality('FISCAL_YEAR') }};q = filter q by {{ column(CITY_1.selection, [\"CITY\"]).asEquality('CITY') }};q = filter q by {{ column(BUILDING_1.selection, [\"BUILDING\"]).asEquality('BUILDING') }};q = filter q by {{ column(OFFICE_TYPE_1.selection, [\"OFFICE_TYPE\"]).asEquality('OFFICE_TYPE') }};q = group q by ('CITY','BUILDING');q = foreach q generate 'CITY' as 'CITY', 'BUILDING' as 'BUILDING', sum('RSF') as 'sum_RSF', sum('RSF') * 0.092903 as 'sum_RSM';q = order q by 'sum_RSF' desc;","measures":[["sum","{{cell(static_1.selection, 0, \"value\").asObject()}}"]],"groups":["CITY","BUILDING"]}

{"pigql":"q = load \"AnnualRentObligationReport\"; q = filter q by EXPENSE_INCOME not in [\"INCOME\"]; q = group q by FISCAL_YEAR; q = foreach q generate FISCAL_YEAR, sum(RSF) as sum_RSF, sum(RSF) * 0.092903 as sum_RSM;","measures":[["sum","{{cell(static_1.selection, 0, \"value\").asObject()}}",null,{"display":" "}]],"autoFilter":true,"groups":["FISCAL_YEAR"]}
